name: NotSoNice-Space Travel
description:
Saddle down your rocket and get ready for this mind wrecking race through the asteroids! Collect stars and earn a reputation as a hard boiled space cowboy or -girl in the harsh world of astronauts!

- High score
- 3D-Graphics
- SPACE - Boost

There might be a bug or two, but i will constantly keep this up to date.

Hi! I'm Antti, "proud" developer of this masterpiece ;)

I'm currently studying in game dev. and this is my first ever build, feel free to leave a comment, i'ts highly appreciated!

Thank you and Enjoy <3
